cis.monopoly.gameDrawers

Class DiceDrawer

  • java.lang.Object
    • cis.monopoly.gameDrawers.DiceDrawer

  • public final class DiceDrawer
extends java.lang.Object

    DiceDrawer

    Draws the two dice on the window based off the roll of the Dice class contained within the GameController class.
    Version:
    0.6
    Author:
    Kyle Turske
